replies.txt_content:
 本帖最后由 林言呀 于 2020-5-7 11:30 编辑 

事件执行的话:
Player player = event.getplayer;
player.setFlying(true);
指令执行的话:
Player player = (Player) commandSender;
player.setFlying(true);

前提是注册了事件和指令
